OL,4,Csurgery at SWAH closed
OL,6,FThe Western Trust board has decided to
OL,7,Fclose the current public consultation
OL,8,Fon the permanent removal of emergency
OL,9,Fgeneral surgery at the South West
OL,10,FAcute Hospital (SWAH) after it was
OL,11,Fpaused in July by Health Minister Mike
OL,12,FNesbitt.
OL,14,FThe announcement came following a
OL,15,Fprivate meeting of the board on
OL,16,FTuesday.
OL,18,FEmergency general surgery at the
OL,19,Fhospital was first suspended in
OL,20,FDecember 2022.
