OL,6,FOne retired consultant cardiologist
OL,7,Fwho helped establish the hospital more
OL,8,Fthan 10 years ago has told UTV he is
OL,9,Fdisappointed by what is happening.
OL,11,FProfessor Mahendra Varma OBE was one
OL,12,Fof the architects of the SWAH when it
OL,13,Fopened in 2012.
OL,15,FHe is frustrated at what has happened
OL,16,Fat the Enniskillen site from a
OL,17,Fpersonal perspective.
OL,19,FIn 2022, the Western Trust temporarily
OL,20,Fsuspended emergency general surgery
OL,21,Fblaming a shortage of surgeons.
