OL,6,F"Knowing the track record of the
OL,7,Fhealth service, when they say
OL,8,Ftemporary, to me it's parenthesis for
OL,9,Fsaying permanent.
OL,11,F"I'm very disappointed with the way it
OL,12,Fhas gone.
OL,14,F"I'm now retired, going on almost 10
OL,15,Fyears. At the time of my retirement,
OL,16,Fthere was a full complement of all
OL,17,Fstaff in the hospital.
