OL,6,F"A number of my colleagues who worked
OL,7,Fwith me live in Enniskillen and now
OL,8,Fwork across the border. So that must
OL,9,Fsay something", Professor Varma told
OL,10,FUTV.
OL,12,FFigures show in 2023 the Trust
OL,13,Fadvertised and recruited two temporary
OL,14,Fsurgeons.
OL,16,FThose surgeons remain engaged on an
OL,17,F"as needed" trust-wide locum contract
OL,18,Ffor planned surgery, the Trust
OL,19,Fconfirmed.
