OL,6,FIn 2024, a team travelled to Mumbai on
OL,7,Fa recruitment drive through which they
OL,8,Fsecured two short term Consultant
OL,9,FSurgeons and five Speciality Doctors
OL,10,Fwith trust-wide responsibilities.
OL,12,FIn July, Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,13,Fpaused a consultation by the Trust to
OL,14,Fpermanently remove the service.
OL,16,FFollowing a Trust board meeting on
OL,17,FTuesday, the decision was made to
OL,18,Fclose the consultation altogether.
